===Noun===
'''theme''' (''plural:'' [[themes]])

# a [[subject]] of a [[talk]] or an [[artistic]] piece; a [[topic]].
# a [[recurring]] [[motif]].
#{{music}} the main [[melody]] of a piece of [[music]], especially one that is the source of [[variation]]s.

